  <summary date="2019-03-25T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Protecting Military Firefighters from PFAS Act

This bill requires the Department of Defense (DOD) to provide blood testing, during annual physical examinations of DOD firefighters, to determine and document exposure to perfluoroalkyl and polyfluoroalkyl substances.</summary>
